  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/KeyPair-4815.pem
  IdentitiesOnly yes

Host termux
  HostName samsung
  User u0_a737
  Port 8022

# 基本连接：Host、HostName、User、Port
# 密钥与代理：IdentityFile、IdentitiesOnly、AddKeysToAgent、IdentityAgent、ForwardAgent
# 跳板/代理：ProxyJump (JumpHost)、ProxyCommand
# 保活：ServerAliveInterval、ServerAliveCountMax、TCPKeepAlive
# 连接复用：ControlMaster、ControlPath、ControlPersist
# 安全与日志：StrictHostKeyChecking、UserKnownHostsFile、HashKnownHosts、LogLevel
# 算法与压缩：Ciphers、KexAlgorithms、HostKeyAlgorithms、Compression
# 转发：LocalForward、RemoteForward、DynamicForward (SOCKS)
# TTY/命令：RequestTTY、RemoteCommand、PermitLocalCommand、LocalCommand
# 选择与拆分：Match、Include、CanonicalizeHostname、CanonicalDomains
# 认证方式：PreferredAuthentications、GSSAPIAuthentication